mentioning the name ali a shiite saint in prayer calls 
sermons are banned in most mosques and its impossible to get 
permission to build new mosques shiites said 
any violation is considered a political act and leads to 
imprisonment the shiites said 
all saudis are part of society and have to respect the 
feelings of the majority said a saudi prince speaking on 
condition he not be named 
