foreseeable future but jordan has it all magnificently organized 
its time for us to go home 
shaalan i which once contained about 45000 people fleeing 
kuwait and iraq closed on thursday mercy camp tents emptied 
sunday the government has said it will set up a small border 
receiving station for new refugees 
