symbionese liberation army 
in 1987 president reagan announced that he and soviet leader 
mikhail gorbachev would meet later in the year to sign a treaty 
banning medium and shorterrange nuclear missiles 
ten years ago president jimmy carter told a news conference the 
united states was not going to apologize for past actions in 
iran pulitzer prizewinning author katherine anne porter died in 
