for the order to protect trade secrets and employee confidentiality 
and to prevent a repeat of statements made by citizens after a tour 
of thermalkems facility in 1989 after that tour members of the 
group said they became ill at the plant 
the environmental groups and the herald newspaper of rock hill 
are opposing the order 
