race car driver bobby rahal is balding wears glasses and is in 
short not your typical race car driver but his father once told 
an interviewer its in the genes the arab people the lebanese 
especially always run scared thats what drives us were more 
afraid of failure than anything its an ego thing we hate the 
flavor of failure and we revel in success 
there is also selwa lucky roosevelt she is like casey kasem 
a druze married to former cia officer archibald bulloch roosevelt 
