under the projected guidelines for doing the research goldstein 
says the mother would give permission for aborted tissue to be 
used but wouldnt know if it were used also neither the doctor 
doing the tissue transplant nor the recipient of the tissue would 
know where it came from 
from my standpoint i think it is an experiment worth doing 
under experimental conditions he says the reason i wanted it 
done at nih is that it would be done under the spotlight of public 
scrutiny 
