the 81500 us price tag the company estimates that if you 
rented the same car for a month youd pay 5600 
some us dealers offer deep discounts almost equalling european 
prices but they cant match travel incentives 
overseas delivery plans offered only to us residents require 
customers to order and prepay before leaving for europe 
personally pick up cars with documents and passport in hand and 
within a specified time period ship cars home to local dealers 
where cars can be picked up eight to 10 weeks later 
a key attraction is getting the most appealing make and model 
