firstquarter gains in sales and operating profits of 15 percent 
and 18 percent respectively 
the performance was led by betty crocker products big g cereals 
and international food operations betty crocker benefited from 
volume gains of 11 percent for desserts 14 percent for hamburger 
helper and other main meal mixes and more than 50 percent for 
various snack food categories atwater said 
